After a lot of work, I'm glad to preset the beta version 1.0 of Weapon Stats Configurator!

This mutator allows you to configure:

- Max Dmg
- Cost
- Weight
- HeadShot multiplier
- Magazine Size
- Reload Speed
- Reload Animation Speed
- Fire Rate
- Fire Rate Animation speed

Of any Killing Floor Standard weapon!

Currently, only SS (SharpShooter) and Medic weapons are supported. This mutator will grow to support all other perk and off-perk weapons whenever i have time to update it!


[b][u]Features that will be added[/u][/b]

- All other perk weapons
- Possible any requested option of a weapon, such as Trader UI damage bar, ammo cost etc..

[b][u]Number Of Files[/u][/b]

- 2

[b][u]File Names[/u][/b]

- \System\KFWeaponStatConfig.u
- \System\KFWeaponStatConfig.ucl

[b][u]Usage[/u][/b]

1- Subscribe or download manually (recommended)
2- Launch the game and wait to see 'Completed'
3- Restart the game and you can see the mutators in your list

[b][u]Class Names[/u][/b]

- Spawn Mut: KFWeaponStatConfig.KFWeaponStatConfig

[b][u]Known Bugs[/u][/b]

You Tell Me.

